--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-10-26)
C: Set '--no-auth' by default (to activate, create: /data/rest-server/.htpasswd)
B: Update file name to upstream naming
B: Update unarchive tasks to support format change (from .gz to .tar.gz)

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-10-26)
F: Update 'rest-server' to version '0.10.0'

* Version 0.1.5 (2020-07-21)
E: Move service user's home directory to '/var/empty/rest-server'

* Version 0.1.4 (2020-07-17)
B: Correct POSIX owner and group of rest-server data directory
E: Improve POSIX permissions of rest-server data directory

* Version 0.1.3 (2020-07-17)
B: Rename data directory variables

* Version 0.1.2 (2020-07-17)
C: Move rest-server backup path to '/data/rest-server'

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-07-17)
B: Remove double quotes from path parameter

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-07-15)
F: Initial release
